rows.label: xs33520100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Maaaaaannnn...! You would not believe
how glad I am to see you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33520100_MSG0020
rows.name:
I woke up all by my lonesome here on enemy turf,
and I was PA-NIC-KING![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33520100_MSG0030
rows.name:
But hey, I'm glad you're all right.
There's still everything to play for, isn't there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33520100_MSG0040
rows.name: Let's hurry on over to kick Void's butt, and save Al.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33520100_MSG0050
rows.name:
And then, we'll head back,
and we'll get a real heroes' welcome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33520100_MSG0060
rows.name:
I believe in us.
One more push, and we're home free.[ST:wait ]
